{"mn98:0.1":"Majjhima Nikaya 98 ","mn98:0.2":"Vasetthasutta ","mn98:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","mn98:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava icchanangale viharati icchanangalavanasande. ","mn98:2.1":"Tena kho pana samayena sambahula abhinnata abhinnata brahmanamahasala icchanangale pativasanti, seyyathidam—","mn98:2.2":"canki brahmano, tarukkho brahmano, pokkharasati brahmano, janussoni brahmano, todeyyo brahmano, anne ca abhinnata abhinnata brahmanamahasala. ","mn98:3.1":"Atha kho vasetthabharadvajanam manavanam janghaviharam anucankamantanam anuvicarantanam ayamantarakatha udapadi: ","mn98:3.2":"“katham, bho, brahmano hoti”ti? ","mn98:3.3":"Bharadvajo manavo evamaha: ","mn98:3.4":"“yato kho, bho, ubhato sujato matito ca pitito ca samsuddhagahaniko yava sattama pitamahayuga akkhitto anupakkuttho jativadena—","mn98:3.5":"ettavata kho, bho, brahmano hoti”ti. ","mn98:3.6":"Vasettho manavo evamaha: ","mn98:3.7":"“yato kho, bho, silava ca hoti vattasampanno ca—","mn98:3.8":"ettavata kho, bho, brahmano hoti”ti. ","mn98:4.1":"Neva kho asakkhi bharadvajo manavo vasettham manavam sannapetum, na pana asakkhi vasettho manavo bharadvajam manavam sannapetum. ","mn98:5.1":"Atha kho vasettho manavo bharadvajam manavam amantesi: ","mn98:5.2":"“ayam kho, bho bharadvaja, samano gotamo sakyaputto sakyakula pabbajito icchanangale viharati icchanangalavanasande. ","mn98:5.3":"Tam kho pana bhavantam gotamam evam kalyano kittisaddo abbhuggato: ","mn98:5.4":"‘itipi so bhagava araham sammasambuddho vijjacaranasampanno sugato lokavidu anuttaro purisadammasarathi sattha devamanussanam buddho bhagava’ti. ","mn98:5.5":"Ayama, bho bharadvaja, yena samano gotamo tenupasankamissama; upasankamitva samanam gotamam etamattham pucchissama. ","mn98:5.6":"Yatha no samano gotamo byakarissati tatha nam dharessama”ti. ","mn98:5.7":"“Evam, bho”ti kho bharadvajo manavo vasetthassa manavassa paccassosi. ","mn98:6.1":"Atha kho vasetthabharadvaja manava yena bhagava tenupasankamimsu; upasankamitva bhagavata saddhim sammodimsu. ","mn98:6.2":"Sammodaniyam katham saraniyam vitisaretva ekamantam nisidimsu. ","mn98:6.3":"Ekamantam nisinno kho vasettho manavo bhagavantam gathahi ajjhabhasi: ","mn98:7.1":"“Anunnatapatinnata, ","mn98:7.2":"tevijja mayamasmubho; ","mn98:7.3":"Aham pokkharasatissa, ","mn98:7.4":"tarukkhassayam manavo. ","mn98:7.5":"Tevijjanam yadakkhatam, ","mn98:7.6":"tatra kevalinosmase; ","mn98:7.7":"Padakasma veyyakarana, ","mn98:7.8":"jappe acariyasadisa; ","mn98:7.9":"Tesam no jativadasmim, ","mn98:7.10":"vivado atthi gotama. ","mn98:7.11":"Jatiya brahmano hoti, ","mn98:7.12":"bharadvajo iti bhasati; ","mn98:7.13":"Ahanca kammuna brumi, ","mn98:7.14":"evam janahi cakkhuma. ","mn98:7.15":"Te na sakkoma napetum, ","mn98:7.16":"annamannam mayam ubho; ","mn98:7.17":"Bhavantam putthumagama, ","mn98:7.18":"sambuddham iti vissutam. ","mn98:7.19":"Candam yatha khayatitam, ","mn98:7.20":"pecca panjalika jana; ","mn98:7.21":"Vandamana namassanti, ","mn98:7.22":"lokasmim gotamam. ","mn98:7.23":"Cakkhum loke samuppannam, ","mn98:7.24":"mayam pucchama gotamam; ","mn98:7.25":"Jatiya brahmano hoti, ","mn98:7.26":"udahu bhavati kammuna; ","mn98:7.27":"Ajanatam no pabruhi, ","mn98:7.28":"yatha janemu brahmanan”ti. ","mn98:8.1":"“Tesam vo aham byakkhissam, ","mn98:8.2":"(vasetthati bhagava) ","mn98:8.3":"Anupubbam yathatatham; ","mn98:8.4":"Jativibhangam pananam, ","mn98:8.5":"Annamannahi jatiyo. ","mn98:8.6":"Tinarukkhepi janatha, ","mn98:8.7":"na capi patijanare; ","mn98:8.8":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","mn98:8.9":"annamanna hi jatiyo. ","mn98:8.10":"Tato kite patange ca, ","mn98:8.11":"yava kunthakipillike; ","mn98:8.12":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","mn98:8.13":"annamanna hi jatiyo. ","mn98:8.14":"Catuppadepi janatha, ","mn98:8.15":"khuddake ca mahallake; ","mn98:8.16":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","mn98:8.17":"annamanna hi jatiyo. ","mn98:8.18":"Padudarepi janatha, ","mn98:8.19":"urage dighapitthike; ","mn98:8.20":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","mn98:8.21":"annamanna hi jatiyo. ","mn98:8.22":"Tato macchepi janatha, ","mn98:8.23":"udake varigocare; ","mn98:8.24":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","mn98:8.25":"annamanna hi jatiyo. ","mn98:8.26":"Tato pakkhipi janatha, ","mn98:8.27":"pattayane vihangame; ","mn98:8.28":"Lingam jatimayam tesam, ","mn98:8.29":"annamanna hi jatiyo. ","mn98:9.1":"Yatha etasu jatisu, ","mn98:9.2":"lingam jatimayam puthu; ","mn98:9.3":"Evam natthi manussesu, ","mn98:9.4":"lingam jatimayam puthu. ","mn98:9.5":"Na kesehi na sisehi, ","mn98:9.6":"na kannehi na akkhihi; ","mn98:9.7":"Na mukhena na nasaya, ","mn98:9.8":"na otthehi bhamuhi va. ","mn98:9.9":"Na givaya na amsehi, ","mn98:9.10":"na udarena na pitthiya; ","mn98:9.11":"Na soniya na urasa, ","mn98:9.12":"na sambadhe na methune. ","mn98:9.13":"Na hatthehi na padehi, ","mn98:9.14":"nangulihi nakhehi va; ","mn98:9.15":"Na janghahi na uruhi, ","mn98:9.16":"na vannena sarena va; ","mn98:9.17":"Lingam jatimayam neva, ","mn98:9.18":"yatha annasu jatisu. ","mn98:9.19":"Paccattanca sariresu, ","mn98:9.20":"manussesvetam na vijjati; ","mn98:9.21":"Vokaranca manussesu, ","mn98:9.22":"samannaya pavuccati. ","mn98:10.1":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","mn98:10.2":"gorakkham upajivati; ","mn98:10.3":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","mn98:10.4":"kassako so na brahmano. ","mn98:10.5":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","mn98:10.6":"puthusippena jivati; ","mn98:10.7":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","mn98:10.8":"sippiko so na brahmano. ","mn98:10.9":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","mn98:10.10":"voharam upajivati; ","mn98:10.11":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","mn98:10.12":"vanijo so na brahmano. ","mn98:10.13":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","mn98:10.14":"parapessena jivati; ","mn98:10.15":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","mn98:10.16":"pessako so na brahmano. ","mn98:10.17":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","mn98:10.18":"adinnam upajivati; ","mn98:10.19":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","mn98:10.20":"coro eso na brahmano. ","mn98:10.21":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","mn98:10.22":"issattham upajivati; ","mn98:10.23":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","mn98:10.24":"yodhajivo na brahmano. ","mn98:10.25":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","mn98:10.26":"porohiccena jivati; ","mn98:10.27":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","mn98:10.28":"yajako so na brahmano. ","mn98:10.29":"Yo hi koci manussesu, ","mn98:10.30":"gamam ratthanca bhunjati; ","mn98:10.31":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","mn98:10.32":"raja eso na brahmano. ","mn98:11.1":"Na caham brahmanam brumi, ","mn98:11.2":"yonijam mattisambhavam; ","mn98:11.3":"Bhovadi nama so hoti, ","mn98:11.4":"sace hoti sakincano; ","mn98:11.5":"Akincanam anadanam, ","mn98:11.6":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.7":"Sabbasamyojanam chetva, ","mn98:11.8":"yo ve na paritassati; ","mn98:11.9":"Sangatigam visamyuttam, ","mn98:11.10":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.11":"Chetva naddhim varattanca, ","mn98:11.12":"sandanam sahanukkamam; ","mn98:11.13":"Ukkhittapaligham buddham, ","mn98:11.14":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.15":"Akkosam vadhabandhanca, ","mn98:11.16":"aduttho yo titikkhati; ","mn98:11.17":"Khantibalam balanikam, ","mn98:11.18":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.19":"Akkodhanam vatavantam, ","mn98:11.20":"silavantam anussadam; ","mn98:11.21":"Dantam antimasariram, ","mn98:11.22":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.23":"Varipokkharapatteva, ","mn98:11.24":"araggeriva sasapo; ","mn98:11.25":"Yo na limpati kamesu, ","mn98:11.26":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.27":"Yo dukkhassa pajanati, ","mn98:11.28":"idheva khayamattano; ","mn98:11.29":"Pannabharam visamyuttam, ","mn98:11.30":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.31":"Gambhirapannam medhavim, ","mn98:11.32":"maggamaggassa kovidam; ","mn98:11.33":"Uttamatthamanuppattam, ","mn98:11.34":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.35":"Asamsattham gahatthehi, ","mn98:11.36":"anagarehi cubhayam; ","mn98:11.37":"Anokasarimappiccham, ","mn98:11.38":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.39":"Nidhaya dandam bhutesu, ","mn98:11.40":"tasesu thavaresu ca; ","mn98:11.41":"Yo na hanti na ghateti, ","mn98:11.42":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.43":"Aviruddham viruddhesu, ","mn98:11.44":"attadandesu nibbutam; ","mn98:11.45":"Sadanesu anadanam, ","mn98:11.46":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.47":"Yassa rago ca doso ca, ","mn98:11.48":"mano makkho ca ohito; ","mn98:11.49":"Sasaporiva aragga, ","mn98:11.50":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.51":"Akakkasam vinnapanim, ","mn98:11.52":"giram saccam udiraye; ","mn98:11.53":"Yaya nabhisajje kinci, ","mn98:11.54":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.55":"Yo ca digham va rassam va, ","mn98:11.56":"anum thulam subhasubham; ","mn98:11.57":"Loke adinnam nadeti, ","mn98:11.58":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.59":"Asa yassa na vijjanti, ","mn98:11.60":"asmim loke paramhi ca; ","mn98:11.61":"Nirasasam visamyuttam, ","mn98:11.62":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.63":"Yassalaya na vijjanti, ","mn98:11.64":"annaya akathankathim; ","mn98:11.65":"Amatogadham anuppattam, ","mn98:11.66":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.67":"Yodhapunnanca papanca, ","mn98:11.68":"ubho sangam upaccaga; ","mn98:11.69":"Asokam virajam suddham, ","mn98:11.70":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.71":"Candam va vimalam suddham, ","mn98:11.72":"vippasannam anavilam; ","mn98:11.73":"Nandibhavaparikkhinam, ","mn98:11.74":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.75":"Yo imam palipatham duggam, ","mn98:11.76":"samsaram mohamaccaga; ","mn98:11.77":"Tinno parangato jhayi, ","mn98:11.78":"anejo akathankathi; ","mn98:11.79":"Anupadaya nibbuto, ","mn98:11.80":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.81":"Yodhakame pahantvana, ","mn98:11.82":"anagaro paribbaje; ","mn98:11.83":"Kamabhavaparikkhinam, ","mn98:11.84":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.85":"Yodhatanham pahantvana, ","mn98:11.86":"anagaro paribbaje; ","mn98:11.87":"Tanhabhavaparikkhinam, ","mn98:11.88":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.89":"Hitva manusakam yogam, ","mn98:11.90":"dibbam yogam upaccaga; ","mn98:11.91":"Sabbayogavisamyuttam, ","mn98:11.92":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.93":"Hitva ratinca aratim, ","mn98:11.94":"sitibhutam nirupadhim; ","mn98:11.95":"Sabbalokabhibhum viram, ","mn98:11.96":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.97":"Cutim yo vedi sattanam, ","mn98:11.98":"upapattinca sabbaso; ","mn98:11.99":"Asattam sugatam buddham, ","mn98:11.100":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.101":"Yassa gatim na jananti, ","mn98:11.102":"deva gandhabbamanusa; ","mn98:11.103":"Khinasavam arahantam, ","mn98:11.104":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.105":"Yassa pure ca paccha ca, ","mn98:11.106":"majjhe ca natthi kincanam; ","mn98:11.107":"Akincanam anadanam, ","mn98:11.108":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.109":"Usabham pavaram viram, ","mn98:11.110":"mahesim vijitavinam; ","mn98:11.111":"Anejam nhatakam buddham, ","mn98:11.112":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:11.113":"Pubbenivasam yo vedi, ","mn98:11.114":"saggapayanca passati; ","mn98:11.115":"Atho jatikkhayam patto, ","mn98:11.116":"tamaham brumi brahmanam. ","mn98:12.1":"Samanna hesa lokasmim, ","mn98:12.2":"namagottam pakappitam; ","mn98:12.3":"Sammucca samudagatam, ","mn98:12.4":"tattha tattha pakappitam. ","mn98:12.5":"Digharattanusayitam, ","mn98:12.6":"ditthigatamajanatam; ","mn98:12.7":"Ajananta no pabrunti, ","mn98:12.8":"jatiya hoti brahmano. ","mn98:12.9":"Na jacca brahmano hoti, ","mn98:12.10":"na jacca hoti abrahmano; ","mn98:12.11":"Kammuna brahmano hoti, ","mn98:12.12":"kammuna hoti abrahmano. ","mn98:12.13":"Kassako kammuna hoti, ","mn98:12.14":"sippiko hoti kammuna; ","mn98:12.15":"Vanijo kammuna hoti, ","mn98:12.16":"pessako hoti kammuna. ","mn98:12.17":"Coropi kammuna hoti, ","mn98:12.18":"yodhajivopi kammuna; ","mn98:12.19":"Yajako kammuna hoti, ","mn98:12.20":"rajapi hoti kammuna. ","mn98:13.1":"Evametam yathabhutam, ","mn98:13.2":"kammam passanti pandita; ","mn98:13.3":"Paticcasamuppadadassa, ","mn98:13.4":"kammavipakakovida. ","mn98:13.5":"Kammuna vattati loko, ","mn98:13.6":"kammuna vattati paja; ","mn98:13.7":"Kammanibandhana satta, ","mn98:13.8":"rathassaniva yayato. ","mn98:13.9":"Tapena brahmacariyena, ","mn98:13.10":"samyamena damena ca; ","mn98:13.11":"Etena brahmano hoti, ","mn98:13.12":"etam brahmanamuttamam. ","mn98:13.13":"Tihi vijjahi sampanno, ","mn98:13.14":"santo khinapunabbhavo; ","mn98:13.15":"Evam vasettha janahi, ","mn98:13.16":"brahma sakko vijanatan”ti. ","mn98:14.1":"Evam vutte, vasetthabharadvaja manava bhagavantam etadavocum: ","mn98:14.2":"“abhikkantam, bho gotama, abhikkantam, bho gotama. ","mn98:14.3":"Seyyathapi, bho gotama, nikkujjitam va ukkujjeyya, paticchannam va vivareyya, mulhassa va maggam acikkheyya, andhakare va telapajjotam dhareyya ‘cakkhumanto rupani dakkhanti’ti; evamevam bhota gotamena anekapariyayena dhammo pakasito. ","mn98:14.4":"Ete mayam bhavantam gotamam saranam gacchama dhammanca bhikkhusanghanca. ","mn98:14.5":"Upasake no bhavam gotamo dharetu ajjatagge panupetam saranam gate”ti. ","mn98:14.6":"Vasetthasuttam nitthitam atthamam. "}